{"word":"Language","slug":"language","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Language</b> Unity of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=1'>Gen 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=6'>Gen 11:6</a><br/> Confusion of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=9'>Gen 11:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=5'>Gen 10:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=20'>Gen 10:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=31'>Gen 10:31</a><br/> Dialects of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=12&verse=6'>Jdg 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=73'>Mat 26:73</a><br/> Many spoken at Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=20'>Joh 19:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=11'>Act 2:11</a><br/> Speaking in an unknown language in religious assemblies, forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=14&verse=28'>1Co 14:28</a><br/> Gift of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=17'>Mar 16:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=8'>Act 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=46'>Act 10:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=6'>Act 19:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=12&verse=10'>1Co 12:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=14'>1Ch 14</a><br/> Mentioned in scripture:<br/> - Of Ashdod<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=24'>Neh 13:24</a> <br/> - Chaldee<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=4'>Dan 1:4</a> <br/> - Egyptian<br/> <a href='h